+{
+  "baseRefName": "main",
+  "baseRefOid": "e1349a76da02dfbac0909a3233bb9e44fc3cd637",
+  "body": "## Summary\nAdds the `--use-agent-commander` option to both `solve.mjs` and `hive.mjs`. When enabled, this experimental flag delegates tool execution to the [agent-commander](https://github.com/link-assistant/agent-commander) library instead of using the embedded tool logic in this repository.\n\nFixes #1043\n\n## Changes\n- Added `--use-agent-commander` option to `solve.config.lib.mjs` (hidden, experimental)\n- Added `--use-agent-commander` option to `hive.config.lib.mjs` (hidden, experimental)\n- Created `agent-commander.lib.mjs` wrapper library with:\n  - `isAgentCommanderAvailable()` - Checks if agent-commander is installed\n  - `validateAgentCommanderConnection()` - Validates tool connection\n  - `executeWithAgentCommander()` - Unified execution interface\n  - `checkForUncommittedChanges()` - Git status checking\n- Integrated agent-commander in `solve.mjs` tool execution flow (first priority check when flag enabled)\n- Passed `--use-agent-commander` flag through `hive.mjs` to solve workers\n- Added `agent-commander` as optional dependency in `package.json`\n- Added experiment scripts for testing the integration\n\n## Behavior\nThe option is:\n- Hidden from `--help` output (experimental feature)\n- Disabled by default (opt-in only)\n- Fails gracefully with clear error message when agent-commander is not installed\n\n## Usage\n```bash\n# Install agent-commander (required for the flag to work)\nnpm install agent-commander\n\n# Use with solve.mjs\nsolve.mjs https://github.com/owner/repo/issues/123 --use-agent-commander\n\n# Use with hive.mjs\nhive.mjs https://github.com/owner/repo --use-agent-commander\n```\n\n## Test plan\n- [x] Verify `--use-agent-commander` option is hidden from `--help`\n- [x] Verify lint and format checks pass\n- [x] Verify baseline functionality works without the flag\n- [x] Verify availability detection works (shows clear message when not installed)\n- [x] Verify graceful failure when agent-commander is not installed\n\n🤖 Generat